f%20the%20children's%20parents%20reported%20him%20to%20the%20police%20for%20inappropriately%20touching%20her%20eight-year-old%20son.%20Further%20police%20investigation%20subsequently%20revealed%2011%20victims%20across%20Southern%20California%20dating%20back%20to%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20court%2C%20the%20Orange%20County%20District%20Attorney%20described%20Zakrzewski%20as%20a%20''monster%20disguised%20by%20smiles%20and%20giggles''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''This%20is%20a%20case%20of%20shattered%20innocence%20and%20precious%20childhoods%20that%20were%20robbed%20from%2017%20little%20boys.%20These%20children%20will%20never%20know%20the%20people%20they%20were%20truly%20intended%20to%20be%20%E2%80%93%20because%20their%20childhoods%20were%20suddenly%20and%20inexplicably%20interrupted%20not%20by%20a%20wolf%20at%20the%20door%2C%20but%20by%20a%20predator%20masquerading%20as%20a%20godsend%2C''%20Orange%20County%20District%20Attorney%20Todd%20Spitzer%20said.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''He%20had%20no%20interest%20in%20protecting%20these%20children%3B%20his%20only%20interest%20was%20in%20preying%20on%20their%20innocence%20and%20filming%20the%20assaults%20for%20his%20sick%20sexual%20gratification%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Spitzer%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20being%20remorseful%2C%20Zakrzewski%20said%2C%20''I%20prided%20myself%20on%20bringing%20smiles%20to%20your%20children%20and%20all%20the%20good%20times%20we%20shared%20were%20100%20percent%20genuine%2C''%20in%20front%20of%20the%20judge.%C2%A0He%20made%20no%20apologies%20to%20the%20victims'%20families%20in%20court%2C%20adding%2C%20''All%20the%20good%20times%20we%20shared%20were%20100%25%20genuine.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Flosangeles%2Fnews%2Fnanny-sentenced-to-707-years-in-prison-for-molesting-kids-and-showing-porn-to-another%2F%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Zakrzewski%20called%20himself%20%26quot%3Bthe%20original%20Sitter%20Buddy%26quot%3B%20and%20offered%20mentorships%2C%20overnight%20and%20vacation%20babysitting%2C%20according%20to%20his%20website.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20more%20than%20six%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20childcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''At%20a%20very%20early%20age%2C%20I%20discovered%20what%20a%20joy%20it%20was%20to%20work%20with%20children%20and%20be%20a%20positive%20impact%20in%20their%20lives%20through%20the%20'Buddy%20Program'%20at%20my%20middle%20school.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20a%20career%20manny%20and%20my%206%2B%20years%20childcare%20experience%20spans%20from%20ages%203%20months%20to%2014%2C%20including%20special%20needs%E2%80%A6%20I%20think%20the%20reason%20I%20connect%20easily%20with%20kids%20is%20because%20I%20am%20not%20just%20there%20to%20supervise%2C%20I%20participate%2C''%20he%20wrote%20on%20his%20website%2C%C2%A0which%20has%20since%20been%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700389320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fk05n29dg_california-male-nann_625x300_19_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-in-california-sentenced-to-707-years-in-prison-for-molesting-16-boys-4586942%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20victims%2C%20aged%202%20to%2014%2C%20were%20under%20Zakrzewski's%20care%20when%20the%20abuses%20took%20place%20and%20all%20of%20the%20crimes%20happened%20between%202014%20and%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-in-california-sentenced-to-707-years-in-prison-for-molesting-16-boys-4586942%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-in-california-sentenced-to-707-years-in-prison-for-molesting-16-boys-4586942%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-in-california-sentenced-to-707-years-in-prison-for-molesting-16-boys-4586942%2Famp%2F1%2