%20for%20their%20excessive%20emphasis%20on%20presentation%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20food%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20an%20X%20user%20shared%20a%20video%20depicting%20Nusret%20Gokce%20preparing%20a%20steak%20at%20one%20of%20his%20restaurants%20and%20performing%20his%20signature%20salt-sprinkling%20technique.%20The%20X%20user%20also%20posted%20an%20alleged%20cost%20breakdown%20of%20a%20bill%20from%20a%20Nusr-Et%20establishment%20below%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20cost%20breakdown%2C%20a%20Sprite%20was%20priced%20at%20%2410%20(approximately%20Rs%20800)%2C%20exceeding%20its%20market%20value%20by%20over%20tenfold.%20A%20dish%20called%20'Golden%20Tomahawk%2C'%20a%20beef%20steak%20wrapped%20in%20gold%20foil%20was%20priced%20at%20%241000%20(approximately%20Rs%2083%2C000).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20concerned%20citizen%20posted%20this%20cost%20breakdown.%20Ten%20bucks%20for%20a%20SPRITE%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FA1fBZnjj4y%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FA1fBZnjj4y%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20South%20Dallas%20Foodie%20(%40SouthDallasFood)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSouthDallasFood%2Fstatus%2F1724885005371846840%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20cost%20breakdown%20sparked%20widespread%20outrage%20among%20internet%20users.%20among%20internet%20users.%20One%20individual%20labelled%20these%20prices%20as%20%26quot%3BOverpriced%20garbage%20for%20the%20uninformed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20netizens%20criticized%20Nusret%20Gokce's%20steak%20preparation%20techniques%20as%20displayed%20in%20the%20video.%20A%20self-proclaimed%20chef%20observed%20that%20Nusret%20Gokce%20sharpened%20a%20steel%20knife%20on%20the%20table%20without%20sanitizing%20it%20before%20slicing%20the%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%