20stay%20with%20me.%20I%20spent%20about%20seven%20months%20out%20of%20the%20year%20in%20Lisbon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20Mexico%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20regularly%20go%20back%20to%20Mexico%2C%20where%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20and%20travel%20often%2C%20so%20I%20was%20familiar%20with%20being%20in%20different%20places.%20But%20I%20realized%20how%20big%20of%20a%20difference%20there%20was%20between%20visiting%20somewhere%20for%20a%20week%20or%20two%20and%20moving%20somewhere.%20You%20may%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20here.%20This%20is%20fantastic%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20living%20in%20that%20place%20is%20very%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20year%20was%20rough.%20My%20girlfriend%20had%20to%20go%20to%20work%20every%20day%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20think%20about%20what%20I%20would%20do%20by%20myself%20all%20day.%20As%20a%20freelancer%2C%20I%20take%20care%20of%20my%20business%20on%20the%20computer%20when%20I'm%20traveling%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20communal%20aspect.%20I%20felt%20lonely%20when%20I%20had%20to%20entertain%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%20home%20from%20work%20and%20on%20the%20weekends%2C%20we%20would%20explore%20the%20city%20like%20tourists%20and%20travel%20around%20the%20area.%20We%20also%20joined%20a%20lot%20of%20expat%20and%20digital-nomad%20communities%20to%20make%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20speak%20Spanish%2C%20I%20had%20difficulty%20with%20Portuguese%2C%20which%20is%20closely%20related.%20Because%20I'm%20a%20photographer%2C%20I%20need%20to%20use%20technical%2C%20specific%20terms%20and%20have%20to%20communicate%20those.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20did%20learn%20the%20language%20and%20it%20got%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20missed%20the%20conveniences%20of%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20you%20have%20Amazon%2C%20which%20is%20available%2024%20hours%20a%20day.%20Or%20you%20can%20go%20to%207-Eleven%20at%203%20a.m.%20and%20get%20a%20USB%20cable%20if%20you%20need%20it.%20It%20doesn't%20work%20like%20that%20in%20other%20countries.%20Most%20electronics%20%E2%80%94%20hard%20drives%2C%20lenses%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%94%20were%20also%20a%20bit%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20years%20went%20on%2C%20I%20became%20more%20prepared%20and%20started%20bringing%20backup%20batteries%2C%20memory%20cards%2C%20and%20even%20a%20lens-cleaning%20kit%2C%20among%20other%20items%2C%20so%20I%20could%20clean%20and%20maintain%20my%20equipment%20on%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20always%20going%20to%20be%20a%20learning%20curve%20in%20a%20new%20place%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20where%20I%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20my%20advice%20for%20moving%20to%20another%20country%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20plans%20to%20move%20to%20another%20country%2C%20I%20recommend%20getting%20good%20internet%20service%20and%20finding%20a%20way%20to%20watch%20your%20favorite%20shows%20and%20movies.%20A%20lot%20of%20streaming%20services%20don't%20work%20or%20have%20different%20titles%20overseas.%20You%20may%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20at%20home%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20so%20find%20a%20way%20to%20watch%20the%20shows%20and%20movies%20you%20enjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20recommend%20learning%20some%20phrases%20in%20the%20language%20of%20whatever%20country%20you're%20going%20to%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20always%20helpful%20and%20people%20love%20it.%20You%20may%20butcher%20some%20words%2C%20but%20the%20person%20will%20most%20likely%20laugh%20it%20off%20and%20tell%20you%20the%20correct%20pronunciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThinking%20about%20money%20is%20also%20important.%20Look%20at%20the%20bank%20fees%20for%20getting%20money%20out%20of%20an%20ATM.%20Also%2C%20look%20into%20money-transferring%20services%20so%20you%20know%20what%20your%20options%20are%20%E2%80%94%20I%20used%20Wise%20because%20Venmo%20and%20Zelle%20are%20usable%20only%20with%20a%20US%20phone%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20time%20living%20partly%20in%20Portugal%20ended%20in%202020%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20relationship%20and%20my%20time%20in%20Portugal%20ended%20after%20three%20years%2C%20but%20I%20have%20no%20regrets.%20I%20learned%20Portuguese%2C%20and%20because%20of%20her%2C%20I%20learned%20some%20Romanian%20as%20well%2C%20which%20opened%20up%20my%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20abroad%20is%20humbling.%20It%20makes%20you%20view%20the%20world%20and%20other%20people's%20issues%20and%20problems%20differently%20from%20how%20you%20would%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20last%20trip%20to%20Portugal%20was%20in%20July%202020.%20I%20thought%20we%20would%20separate%20and%20come%20back%20together%20again%2C%20but%20we%20broke%20up%20while%20we%20were%20apart.%20After%20the%20breakup%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Mexico%20for%20about%20six%20months%2C%20and%20I%20plan%20to%20continue%20traveling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20great%20system%20now%20where%20I%20leave%20Denver%20right%20after%20Christmas%2C%20go%20back%20to%20traveling%20around%20the%20world%2C%20come%20back%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20April%20for%20my%20nephew's%20birthday%2C%20and%20then%20take%20time%20off%20from%20April%20until%20the%20beginning%20of%20September.%20It%20works%20perfectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsplit-time-denver-lisbon-portugal-inconvenient-lonely-isolating-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700388601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655794d922cf74a5739953b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsplit-time-denver-lisbon-portugal-inconvenient-lonely-isolating-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jermaine%20Amado%20was%20visiting%20Lisbon%20in%202017%20when%20he%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20his%20tour%20guide.%20For%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20he%20split%20his%20time%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Portugal.%22%2C%