ion%3EUsed%20cars%20at%20an%20Infiniti%20dealer%20in%20Highlands%20Ranch%2C%20Colorado.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Zalubowski%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20last%20few%20years%20have%20seen%20purchase%20prices%20of%20used%20vehicles%20skyrocket.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20these%20prices%20are%20now%20finally%20starting%20to%20fall%2C%20according%20to%20the%20automotive%20website%20Edmunds.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20website%20shared%20six%20tips%20to%20help%20buyers%20get%20the%20best%20value%20for%20money%20on%20their%20next%20used%20car.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20few%20years%20have%20been%20rough%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-used-cars-are-still-so-expensive-2023-9%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUsed%2520cars%2520are%2520still%2520expensive%2Cin%25202023%252C%2520a%2520study%2520shows.%5C%22%3Eused-vehicle%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20higher%20prices%2C%20less%20inventory%2C%20and%20rising%20interest%20rates.%20Compared%20to%20what%20people%20normally%20expect%20to%20pay%20from%20buying%20used%2C%20it's%20fair%20to%20say%20the%20market%20has%20been%20discouraging.%20But%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-car-prices-getting-cheaper-except-pickup-trucks-2023-10%5C%22%3Ea%20dim%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Edmunds'%20latest%20Used%20Vehicle%20Report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdmunds%20found%20the%20average%20transaction%20price%20for%20a%20used%20vehicle%20was%20%2428%2C935%20in%20the%20third%20quarter.%20While%20that's%20still%20way%20above%20the%20average%20of%20%2420%2C085%20from%20about%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20has%20dropped%20from%20last%20year's%20record%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20new%20vehicle%20prices%20continue%20to%20rise%2C%20making%20used%20vehicles%20more%20appealing%20for%20shoppers%20on%20a%20smaller%20budget.%20Broadly%2C%20the%20difference%20in%20average%20price%20between%20new%20and%20used%20is%20back%20to%20how%20it%20was%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20it's%20still%20wise%20for%20prospective%20used%20vehicle%20buyers%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20getting%20the%20best%20value%20for%20their%20money.%20The%20experts%20at%20Edmunds%20have%20compiled%20six%20important%20tips%20to%20help%20you%20with%20your%20next%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cbr%3E1.%20Compare%20prices%20to%20avoid%20overpaying%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20out%20if%20you're%20getting%20a%20good%20price%20on%20a%20used%20car%20isn't%20as%20hard%20as%20you%20think.%20There%20are%20multiple%20online%20sites%20like%20Edmunds%20that%20compare%20the%20price%20of%20the%20vehicle%20you%20are%20shopping%20for%20with%20others%20that%20are%20for%20sale%20in%20your%20area.%20By%20simply%20searching%20for%20the%20make%20and%20model%20you%20want%2C%20you'll%20know%20if%20you%20are%20paying%20above%2C%20below%2C%20or%20at%20the%20market%20value%20of%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Expand%20your%20search%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20find%20a%20better%20deal%20if%20you%20broaden%20your%20search%20beyond%20local%20dealerships.%20Instead%20of%20driving%20to%20local%20dealerships%2C%20look%20at%20online%20sites%20first%20to%20know%20what%20dealerships%20have%20in%20stock%20before%20you%20go%20there.%20You%20can%20adjust%20the%20search%20parameters%20to%20include%20nearby%20cities%20and%20counties%20that%20might%20have%20better%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Consider%20other%20types%20of%20vehicles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20a%20particular%20brand%2C%20age%2C%20and%20mileage%20you%20typically%20aim%20for%20when%20buying%20a%20used%20vehicle%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20reconsider%20your%20usual%20approach.%20With%20higher%20prices%20and%20interest%20rates%2C%20opting%20for%20a%20higher-mileage%20or%20older%20model%20will%20help%20get%20you%20to%20the%20monthly%20payment%20you%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20decide%20to%20do%20so%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20get%20a%20vehicle%20history%20report%20to%20ensure%20it%20has%20a%20clean%20title%20and%20has%20had%20regular%20maintenance%20visits.%20A%20prepurchase%20inspection%20from%20a%20mechanic%20can%20also%20help%20spot%20potential%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20prefer%20a%20near-new%20vehicle%2C%20then%20consider%20a%20different%20type%20of%20vehicle%20or%20brand%20to%20save%20money.%20Trucks%20and%20SUVs%20are%20popular%20and%20often%20demand%20a%20higher%20price%20than%20sedans%20or%20subcompact%20SUVs.%20If%20you%20don't%20need%20a%20truck%20or%20large%20SUV%2C%20you%20can%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20by%20getting%20something%20smaller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Get%20preapproval%20for%20a%20loan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20the%20lowest%20interest%20rate%20possible%20will%20lower%20your%20monthly%20payments.%20Instead%20of%20taking%20the%20dealership's%20word%20that%20it's%20offering%20the%20best%20rate%2C%20get%20preapproved%20by%20a%20local%20bank%2C%20credit%20union%2C%20or%20online%20lender%20before%20going%20to%20the%20dealership.%20Then%20compare%20all%20the%20rates%20to%20ensure%20you're%20getting%20the%20lowest%20one.%20If%20you%20aren't%20happy%20with%20the%20rate%20you%20received%2C%20you%20might%20be%20able%20to%20refinance%20the%20loan%20later%20if%20rates%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Maximize%20the%20value%20of%20your%20trade-in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20good%20news%20if%20you%20own%20a%20car%20with%20equity.%20Used%20car%20prices%20are%20still%20high%2C%20but%20that%20means%20you%20should%20get%20more%20for%20your%20car%2C%20which%20will%20help%20offset%20the%20higher%20purchase%20price%20of%20your%20next%20vehicle.%20Get%20a%20free%20vehicle%20appraisal%20through%20online%20sites%20like%20Edmunds%20before%20you%20get%20a%20trade-in%20offer%20from%20your%20dealership%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20getting%20a%20fair%20value.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20trade-in%20or%20if%20it%20doesn't%20have%20equity%2C%20consider%20putting%20more%20money%20down%20to%20get%20the%20monthly%20payment%20you%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E6.%20Shop%20certified%20pre-owned%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20be%20harder%20to%20find%20certified%20pre-owned%20vehicles%20in%20today's%20market%2C%20but%20if%20you%20locate%20one%20within%20your%20budget%2C%20we%20recommend%20going%20for%20it.%20Not%20only%20do%20pre-owned%20vehicles%20undergo%20thorough%20inspections%20and%20additional%20reconditioning%20and%20offer%20extended%20warranties%2C%20they%20could%20potentially%20qualify%20for%20interest%20rates%20similar%20to%20those%20for%20new%20cars.%20%3Cbr%3EAlthough%20such%20vehicles%20are%20more%20expensive%2C%20the%20lower%20interest%20rate%20and%20longer%20warranty%20could%20offset%20the%20higher%20price%20over%20the%20course%20of%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEdmunds%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20used-car%20shoppers%20will%20have%20a%20more%20difficult%20time%20finding%20the%20deal%20they%20want%20in%202023%20and%202024.%20But%20if%20you%20make%20a%20few%20compromises%20on%20the%20type%20of%20vehicle%20you%20want%2C%20research%20how%20much%20your%20trade-in%20is%20worth%2C%20and%20compare%20interest%20rates%20and%20local%20prices%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20much%20better%20about%20your%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20provided%20to%20The%20Associated%20Press%20by%20the%20automotive%20website%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D03267d4c4b82f7d73c83e3a3b32126f0d4c6b98522f96242ecb3aed5b123e998%26postID%3D65575caac2e44d869f4c7272%26postSlug%3Dused-car-six-tips-take-advantage-falling-prices-edmunds-2023-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.edmunds.com%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEdmunds%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-car-six-tips-take-advantage-falling-prices-edmunds-2023-1