w%2F105330799.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmali-malian-army-says-it-discovered-mass-grave-in-kidal%2Famp_articleshow%2F105330799.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmali-malian-army-says-it-discovered-mass-grave-in-kidal%2Famp_articleshow%2F105330799.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20Machine%20Works%20Properly...%26quot%3B%3A%20Nitin%20Gadkari's%20Tunnel%20Rescue%20Timeline%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERescue%20teams%20may%20reach%20the%2041%20workers%20stuck%20inside%20an%20Uttarakhand%20tunnel%20for%20over%20170%20hours%20in%20the%20next%20two%20days%20if%20the%20auger%20machine%20drilling%20into%20the%20debris%20block%20works%20properly%2C%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gadkari%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20today%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20tunnel%20collapse%20that%20has%20left%2041%20lives%20hanging%20by%20the%20thread.%20A%20part%20of%20the%20under-construction%20tunnel%20to%20connect%20Uttarkashi%20and%20Yamunotri%20collapsed%20last%20Sunday%20after%20a%20landslide%2C%20trapping%20the%20workers.%20This%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20centre's%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20week%2C%20repeated%20attempts%20to%20rescue%20the%20workers%20have%20failed%20owing%20to%20several%20challenges%2C%20including%20the%20topography%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20rocks%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20workers%20are%20being%20provided%20food%2C%20water%20and%20oxygen%20supply%20as%20rescue%20teams%20work%20overtime%20for%20a%20breakthrough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said%20the%20priority%20is%20to%20keep%20the%20workers%20alive.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20auger%20machine%20works%20properly%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20them%20in%20the%20next%202-2.5%20days.%20Roads%20are%20being%20made%20by%20BRO%20(Border%20Roads%20Organisition)%20to%20bring%20in%20special%20machines.%20Several%20machines%20have%20arrived%20here.%20Two%20auger%20machines%20are%20currently%20working%20to%20carry%20out%20rescue%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20several%20machines%20have%20arrived%20at%20the%20spot%20and%20two%20are%20currently%20working%20to%20rescue%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Dhami%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20his%20government%20to%20ready%20to%20provide%20help%20to%20the%20rescue%20agencies.%C2%A0%26quot%3BSaving%20everyone's%20life%20is%20our%20first%20priority.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20give%20all%20the%20help%20required%20to%20all%20the%20agencies.%20I%20will%20pray%20to%20God%20that%20they%20get%20rescued%20sooner%2C%20as%20their%20trouble%20is%20increasing%20with%20each%20passing%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20from%20multiple%20agencies%20are%20at%20the%20spot%20for%20the%20challenging%20rescue%20operation.%20These%20include%20officials%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20(PMO).%20%26quot%3BThe%20experts%20agree%20that%20instead%20of%20working%20on%20one%20plan%2C%20we%20should%20work%20simultaneously%20on%20five%20plans%20to%20reach%20the%20trapped%20workers%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bhaskar%20Khulbe%2C%20former%20advisor%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khulbe%20said%20the%20workers%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20rescued%20in%20four-five%20days.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20the%20gods%20are%20kind%20enough%2C%20it%20could%20happen%20even%20earlier%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700387100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fnvsb6rco_uttarakhand-tunnel_625x300_19_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3