he%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20has%20prohibited%20the%20production%2C%20storage%2C%20distribution%20and%20sale%20of%20food%20products%20with%20halal%20certification.%20This%20order%2C%20however%2C%20exempts%20products%20manufactured%20for%20export.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20Halal%20certification%20and%20UP's%20ban%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Halal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalal%20is%20an%20Arabic%20word%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bpermissible%26quot%3B.%20Within%20the%20sphere%20of%20the%20Islamic%20belief%20system%2C%20it%20is%20a%20binary%20opposite%20to%20%26quot%3Bharam%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20means%20%26quot%3Bforbidden%26quot%3B.%20For%20Muslims%2C%20Halal%20mostly%20relates%20to%20dietary%20habits%2C%20especially%20the%20processing%20of%20meat.%20Several%20kinds%20of%20cosmetics%20and%20medicines%20are%20also%20considered%20prohibited%20because%20they%20contain%20by-products%20of%20animals%20Muslims%20are%20barred%20from%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Forbidden%2C%20What's%20Not%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPork%20is%20the%20only%20meat%20specifically%20forbidden%20by%20the%20Quran.%20But%20for%20an%20animal%20meat%20to%20pass%20the%20halal%20check%2C%20it%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20processed%20and%20stored%20in%20accordance%20with%20Islamic%20law.%20The%20criteria%20for%20halal%20meat%20includes%20the%20manner%20of%20the%20animal's%20death.%20Vegetarian%20dishes%20are%20generally%20considered%20halal%20unless%20they%20contain%20alcohol.%20The%20prohibition%20extends%20to%20cosmetics%20and%20medicines%2C%20many%20of%20which%20contain%20animal%20by-products.%20There%20is%20an%20exception%2C%20though.%20A%20Muslim%20can%20consume%20a%20non-halal%20food%20item%20only%20if%20%26quot%3Bcompelled%20by%20necessity%20-%20neither%20driven%20by%20desire%20nor%20exceeding%20immediate%20need%26quot%3B%2C%20meaning%20that%20a%20person%20who%20may%20otherwise%20starve%20to%20death%20is%20permitted%20to%20eat%20non-halal%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow's%20Halal%20Meat%20Different%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20global%20bodies%20involved%20in%20the%20supervision%20and%20certification%20of%20Halal%20products%20lay%20down%20guidelines%20for%20the%20criteria%20for%20a%20food%20item%20to%20be%20considered%20halal.%20Department%20of%20Halal%20Certification%20EU%2C%20an%20Irish%20certification%20body%20working%20in%20Europe%2C%20says%20the%20animal%20must%20be%20alive%20at%20the%20time%20of%20slaughter%20to%20qualify%20as%20halal%20meat.%20Apart%20from%20several%20other%20criteria%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20method%20to%20slaughter%2C%20the%20rules%20also%20state%20that%20only%20an%20animal%20slaughtered%20by%20a%20sane%20adult%20Muslim%20would%20be%20halal%2C%20meaning%20that%20meat%20processed%20by%20a%20non-Muslim%20would%20be%20haram.%20Animals%20slaughtered%20in%20machines%20don't%20qualify%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHalal%20Certification%20In%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20does%20not%20have%20a%20mandatory%20halal%20certification%20system%20and%20no%20specific%20labelling%20requirements%20for%20halal%20food%20products%20imported%20into%20India.%20Some%20private%20companies%20give%20out%20halal%20certification%2C%20marking%20products%20permissible.%20These%20organisations%20are%20recognised%20by%20the%20importing%20countries.%20The%20commerce%20ministy%20said%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20meat%20products%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20exported%20as%20'halal%20certified'%20only%20only%20if%20they%20are%20processed%20and%20packaged%20in%20a%20facility%20that%20has%20a%20certificate%20by%20a%20body%20accredited%20by%20a%20board%20of%20Quality%20Council%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Behind%20The%20UP%20Halal%20Ban%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20government's%20order%20says%20halal%20certification%20of%20food%20products%20is%20a%20parallel%20system%20that%20creates%20confusion%20and%20is%20not%20tenable%20under%20Section%2089%20of%20Food%20Law%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Act%2C%20the%20order%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20right%20to%20decide%20the%20quality%20of%20food%20items%20lies%20only%20with%20the%20authorities%20and%20institutions%20given%20in%20Section%2029%20of%20the%20said%20Act%2C%20who%20check%20the%20relevant%20standards%20as%20per%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20certain%20medicines%2C%20medical%20devices%2C%20and%20cosmetic%20products%20are%20reported%20to%20feature%20the%20Halal%20certificate%20on%20their%20packaging%20or%20labelling%20when%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bno%20provisions%20for%20marking%20Halal%20certification%20on%20labels%20in%20the%20government%20rules%20related%20to%20drugs%2C%20medical%20devices%2C%20and%20cosmetics%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20government's%20order%20follows%20a%20complaint%20that%20alleged%20a%20potential%20conspiracy%20to%20ensure%20lower%20sales%20of%20products%20that%20do%20not%20have%20a%20halal%20certificate.%20This%2C%20the%20complaint%2C%20alleged%20was%20harming%20business%20interests%20of%20other%20communities.%20Such%20a%20malicious%20attempt%20not%20only%20seeks%20unfair%20financial%20benefits%20by%20issuing%20Halal%20certificates%20for%20items%20meant%20for%20common%20citizens%20but%20also%20forms%20part%20of%20a%20pre-planned%20strategy%20to%20sow%20class%20hatred%2C%20create%20divisions%20in%20society%2C%20and%20weaken%20the%20country%2C%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20bodies%20named%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%20Jamiat%20Ulama-i-Hind%20Halal%20Trust%2C%20termed%20the%20allegations%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20will%20take%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%20legal%20measures%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20adhere%20to%20government%20regulations%2C%20as%20emphasised%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Industry%20notification%2C%20requiring%20all%20halal%20certification%20bodies%20to%20be%20registered%20by%20NABCB%20(National%20Accreditation%20Board%20for%20Certification%20Bodies%20under%20Quality%20Council%20of%20India)%2C%20a%20milestone%20that%20Jamiat%20Ulama-I-Hind%20Halal%20Trust%20has%20achieved%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700386440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F8t2uficc_grocery-store_625x300_07_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-halal-tag-for-products-why-has-uttar-pradesh-banned-it-4586845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government's%20move%20to%20ban%20products%20with%20a%20halal%20tag%20has%20sparked%20a%20row.%20A%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20has%20prohibited%20the%20production%2C%20storage%2C%20distribution%20and%20sale%20of%20food%20produts%20with%20halal%20certification%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-halal-tag-for-products-why-has-uttar-pradesh-banned-it-4586845%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-halal-tag-for-products-why-has-uttar-pradesh-banned-it-4586845%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-halal-tag-for-products-why-has-uttar-pradesh-banned-it-4586845%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Memphis%20police%20search%20for%20suspect%20after%204%20female%20victims%20killed%2C%201%20wounded%20in%203%20linked%20shootings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700386401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105330661%2Cimgsize-1282021.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-memphis-police-search-for-suspect-after-4-female-victims-killed-and-1-wounded-in-3-linked-shootings%2Farticleshow%