B%22title%22%3A%22Florida%20scientists%20are%20giving%20coral%20IVF%20treatments%20to%20help%20bolster%20dying%20reef%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22coral%20reef%20restoration%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649f28b76e35e9001af927b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECoral%20reefs%20are%20experiencing%20mass%20bleaching%20and%20die-off%20events%20due%20to%20climate%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScientists%20are%20now%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20toughen%20them%20up%20and%20bolster%20their%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20methods%20include%20temperature-controlled%20tanks%20and%20new%20breeding%20methods.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20marine%20heatwaves%20devastated%20the%20coral%20reef%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Florida%2C%20scientists%20are%20now%20considering%20ways%20to%20toughen%20up%20coral%20in%20the%20face%20of%20rising%20ocean%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20record%20marine%20heat%20wave%20this%20past%20summer%2C%20Florida's%20iconic%20coral%20reef%20experienced%20massive%20bleaching%20and%20die-offs.%20One%20estimate%20from%20the%20Florida%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Research%20Institute%20estimated%20that%2060%25%20of%20monitored%20coral%20reefs%20were%20bleached%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20stress%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20coral%20could%20potentially%20die%20off%20if%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foceanservice.noaa.gov%2Ffacts%2Fcoral_bleach.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWhen%2520water%2520is%2520too%2520warm%2Cand%2520are%2520subject%2520to%2520mortality.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estress%20is%20prolonged.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIan%20Enochs%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20coral%20program%20at%20NOAA's%20Atlantic%20Oceanographic%20and%20Meteorological%20Laboratory%2C%20t