-wonders-in-us-you-should-see-before-theyre-gone-2023-8%23coral-reefs-in-florida-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecoral%20reefs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20continue%20to%20decline.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-52661860%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBBC%20reported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20tried%20altering%20the%20algae%20that%20live%20on%20coral%20to%20make%20it%20more%20heat-resistant%2C%20therefore%20making%20coral%20bleaching%20events%20less%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fnatural-wonders-in-us-you-should-see-before-theyre-gone-2023-8%23coral-reefs-in-florida-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebreeding%20coral%20on%20land%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20to%20prevent%20more%20die-offs%20and%20determine%20which%20species%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20survive%20human-induced%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20breed%20these%20corals%20growing%20in%20tanks%20and%20produce%20offspring%20by%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20we%20can%20start%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Baker%2C%20a%20principal%20investigator%20for%20the%20Darpa%20hybrid%20reef%20project%2C%20told%20the%20Journal.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20great%20at%20destroying%20reef%20ecosystems.%20We%20just%20need%20to%20reverse%20that%20trajectory%20and%20become%20great%20at%20restoring%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-scientists-are-giving-coral-ivf-treatments-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700377601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6559998b9c7d23cb3b9d1b9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-scientists-are-giving-coral-ivf-t