scientist%2C%20for%20a%20meeting%20that%20would%20abruptly%20end%20his%20tenure.%20Greg%20Brockman%2C%20co-founder%20and%20board%20chairman%2C%20learned%20of%20his%20removal%20from%20the%20board%20in%20a%20similarly%20abrupt%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20Altman's%20departure%20read%20like%20a%20plot%20twist%20in%20a%20high-stakes%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fimd060g_sam-altman-reuters_625x300_08_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20call%20on%20Google%20Meet%20-%20the%20irony%20of%20using%20a%20competitor's%20platform%20not%20lost%20on%20the%20tech%20community%20-%20served%20as%20the%20stage%20for%20this%20unexpected%20turn.%20In%20her%20tweets%2C%20Kara%20Swisher%20captured%20the%20shock%20and%20confusion%20rippled%20through%20the%20industry%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20board%20members%20who%20voted%20against%20Altman%20felt%20he%20was%20manipulative%20and%20headstrong...%20This%20might%20not%20be%20a%20typical%20SV%20(Silicon%20Valley)%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20who%20had%20become%20the%20face%20of%20AI's%20most%20audacious%20dreams%20was%20unceremoniously%20fired%2C%20setting%20off%20a%20chain%20reaction%20that%20would%20shake%20the%20very%20foundations%20of%20OpenAI.%20This%20company%20promised%20to%20democratise%20AI%20and%20harness%20its%20potential%20for%20the%20greater%20good.%20Yet%2C%20here%20we%20were%2C%20witnessing%20a%20boardroom%20coup%20that%20felt%20more%20like%20a%20scene%20from%20a%20high-stakes%20thriller%20than%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20of%20a%20tech%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20happens%20when%20the%20guardians%20of%20the%20future%20become%20entangled%20in%20their%20own%20human%20dramas%3F%20The%20story%20of%20OpenAI%20is%20not%20just%20about%20technology%3B%20it's%20about%20the%20people%20behind%20it%2C%20their%20dreams%2C%20their%20conflicts%2C%20and%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20actions%20in%20a%20world%20increasingly%20shaped%20by%20the%20AI%20they%20create.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Narrative%20Not%20Penned%20By%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20AI%20scripts%20narratives%2C%20churns%20out%20prose%2C%20and%20even%20crafts%20poetry%2C%20the%20story%20at%20OpenAI%20reminds%20us%20of%20human%20nature's%20complexity%20and%20unpredictability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20palpable.%20OpenAI%2C%20a%20company%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20developing%20AI%20that%20can%20mimic%20human%20creativity%2C%20is%20embroiled%20in%20a%20saga%20that%20no%20machine%20could%20have%20concocted%20(or%20perhaps%20they%20will%2C%20in%20a%20not-so-near-future).%20It's%20all%20about%20ambition%2C%20betrayal%2C%20and%20controversy%20-%20quintessentially%20human%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Shift%20From%20Idealism%20To%20Realism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20journey%20from%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20to%20a%20for-profit%20entity%20reflects%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20the%20AI%20landscape.%20The%20company%20was%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20corporate%20AI%20land%20grab%20following%20Microsoft's%20multi-billion-dollar%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20raises%20critical%20questions%20about%20the%20balance%20between%20innovation%20and%20AI%20ethics%2C%20profit%20and%20purpose%2C%20mirroring%20the%20broader%20tech%20industry's%20struggle%20to%20reconcile%20its%20ideals%20with%20market%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transformation%20was%20gradual%20but%20significant.%20The%20partnership%20with%20Microsoft%20provided%20financial%20backing%20and%20access%20to%20critical%20resources%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20further%20entrenching%20OpenAI%20in%20the%20corporate%20sphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20OpenAI%20navigated%20this%20new%20terrain%2C%20its%20original%20ethos%20of%20openness%20and%20transparency%20began%20to%20wane.%20The%20company%2C%20which%20once%20championed%20sharing%20its%20research%20and%20developments%2C%20started%20adopting%20a%20more%20guarded%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20was%20evident%20in%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20GPT-2%20language%20model.%20Initially%20hesitant%20to%20release%20the%20model%20due%20to%20concerns%20over%20its%20potential%20misuse%2C%20OpenAI%20eventually%20made%20it%20available%20on%20GitHub%2C%20albeit%20with%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Vice%20wrote%20in%20February%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Open%20AI's%20transition%20marked%20a%20retreat%20from%20the%20open-source%20ideals%2C%20raising%20critical%20questions%20about%20the%20future%20trajectory%20of%20AI%20development%20and%20the%20ethical%20considerations%20that%20come%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnearthing%20The%20Past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20past%20incidents%20and%20allegations%20resurfaced%2C%20casting%20a%20shadow%20over%20the%20company's%20dramatic%20narrative.%20These%20revelations%2C%20emerging%20from%20various%20sources%2C%20added%20layers%20of%20complexity%20and%20intrigue%20to%20the%20unfolding%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20striking%20elements%20was%20the%20resurfacing%20of%20tweets%20from%20Annie%20Altman%2C%20dated%20November%2014%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20messages%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20she%20accused%20her%20biological%20siblings%2C%20primarily%20Sam%20Altman%20and%2C%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20Jack%20Altman%2C%20of%20various%20forms%20of%20abuse.%20Her%20call%20for%20legal%20justice%20and%20group%20healing%2C%20as%20she%20sought%20others%20who%20might%20have%20suffered%20similarly%2C%20painted%20a%20starkly%20different%20picture%20of%20the%20Altman%20family%2C%20contrasting%20sharply%20with%20their%20public%20personas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong