%20the%20expressway%20was%20inaugurated%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fpm-modi-inaugurates-phase-1-nagpur-mumbai-samruddhi-mahamarg-expressway-8318513%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20Modi%20in%20December%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20FIR%20was%20registered%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fsamruddhi-expressway-accident-sub-contractors-booked-crane-collapse-kills-8871230%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eagainst%20the%20sub-contractors%20of%20Navayuga%20Engineering%20Company%20Limited%20and%20VSL%20Private%20Limited%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20agencies%20%E2%80%9Chired%20to%20construct%20Package%2016%20of%20Samruddhi%20Expressway%2C%E2%80%9D%20reported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIncome%20Tax%20raid%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENavayuga%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20multi-crore%20company%2C%20found%20itself%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20the%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20government%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20when%20power%20changed%20hands%20from%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20to%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20in%202019.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Jagan%20regime%20seemed%20to%20view%20Navayuga%20as%20%E2%80%98pro-TDP%E2%80%99%20and%20close%20to%20its%20arch%20rival%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20coveted%20projects%20cornered%20by%20Navayuga%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20during%20the%20TDP%20era%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fandhra-govt-retrieves-4700-acres-from-krishnapatnam-infratechs-sez%2Farticleshow%2F71683465.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20suddenly%20taken%20away%20from%20it%20by%20the%20new%20state%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2026%2C%202018%2C%20a%2020-member%20team%20of%20income%20tax%20officials%20from%20New%20Delhi%20zeroed%20onto%20Navayuga.%20They%20swooped%20down%20on%20multiple%20offices%20of%20the%20conglomerate%20across%20the%20state%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20violating%20income%20tax%20rules%20and%20also%20laundering%20money.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20news%20reports%20have%20underlined%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20had%20been%20eyeing%20the%20Krishnapatnam%20Port%20Company%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-inside-the-companys-growth-machine%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efor%20several%20years%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20it%20had%20gone%20to%20a%20company%20of%20the%20Navayuga%20group%20during%20the%20TDP%20era.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Jagan%20Reddy%20then%20taking%20on%20the%20firm%2C%20Adani%20tried%20its%20luck%20once%20more%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esuccessfully%20acquired%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202020%2C%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20under%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20gave%20its%20consent%20to%20the%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zones%20to%20buy%20out%20a%2075%25%20stake%20in%20that%20port%20from%20Navayuga.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Flogistics%2Fadani-ports-takes-full-control-of-krishnapatnam-port%2Farticle34241716.ece%5C%22%3EThe%20remaining%2025%25%20was%20taken%20over%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPlum%20projects%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20tunnel%20is%20on%20the%20Char%20Dham%20route%2C%20a%20pet%20project%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20completed%2C%20it%20would%20not%20only%20shorten%20the%20pilgrimage%20route%20to%20Yamunotri%20by%2020%20kms%2C%20but%20also%20enable%20all-weather%20connectivity%20to%20the%20major%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20site.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20project%2C%20cleared%20by%20the%20cabinet%20committee%20on%20economic%20affairs%20which%20was%20chaired%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%202018%2C%20was%20to%20be%20completed%20in%202022%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1521024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20currently%20on%20an%20extension.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20mid-2020%2C%20Navayuga%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbmcw.com%2Fnews%2Fnavayuga-group-bags-1-887-cr-rail-line-project.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%20been%20granted%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20Rishikesh-Karnaprayag%20rail%20link%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20project.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700325616000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115024%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.50.16%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwho-was-building-the-uttarakhand-tunnel-that-collapsed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20details%20on%20Navayuga%20Engineering%20Company%20Limited%2C%20from%20which%2041%20workers%20remain%20trapped%20in%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20Union%20government's%20high-profile%20yet%20controversial%20Char%20Dham%20project%20in%20Uttarkashi%2C%20are%20worth%20noting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwho-was-building-the-uttarakhand-tunnel-that-collapsed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20IDFA%20Award%20Acceptance%20Speech%2C%20Anand%20Patwardhan%20Calls%20For%20%E2%80%98Immediate%20Ceasefire%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Just%20Peace%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F25093726%2Fanand-patwardhan.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cspan%3EIndian%20documentary%20filmmaker%20Anand%20Patwardhan%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20in%20his%20acceptance%20speech%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2023%2F11%2Fidfa-2023-documentary-awards-winners-1235615852%2F%5C%22%3EBest%20Editing%20award%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20International%20Documentary%20Festival%20Amsterdam%20(IDFA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatwardhan%20won%20the%20award%20for%20his%20film%20titled%20%3Cem%3EVasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%2FThe%20World%20is%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20festival%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20documentary%20gathering%2C%20has%20long%20been%20seen%20as%20being%20politically%20vocal%20and%20has%20come%20under%20criticism%20in%20its%20latest%20edition%20for%20attempting%20to%20tread%20carefully%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20faced%20criticism%20first%20from%20some%20Israeli%20and%20American%20filmmakers%2C%20and%20then%20from%20Palestinian%20filmmakers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EDeadline%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20opening%20night%20ceremony%20of%20the%20festival%20last%20Wednesday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2023%2F11%2Finternational-documentary-festival-amsterdam-israel-gaza-controversy-1235612497%2F%5C%22%3Esaw%20three%20pro-Palestinian%20demonstrators%20interrupting%3C%2Fa%3E%20IDFA%20artistic%20director%20Orwa%20Nyrabia%E2%80%99s%20remarks.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20carrying%20a%20banner%20bearing%20the%20controversial%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20River%20to%20the%20Sea%2C%20Palestine%20Will%20Be%20Free%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20is%20viewed%20by%20many%20Jews%20as%20anti-Semitic%20and%20calling%20for%20the%20destruction%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Nyrabia%20applauded%20the%20protesters%20on%20stage%2C%20he%20later%20issued%20a%20joint%20apology%20after%20facing%20criticism%20from%20members%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20film%20community%20as%20well%20as%20some%20documentary%20filmmakers%20in%20the%20US.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20apology%20then%20drew%20criticism%20from%20many%20Palestinian%20filmmakers%20including%20Basma%20al-Sharif%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20director%20and%20artist%20who%20withdrew%20a%20film%20at%20the%20festival.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPalestinian%20filmmaker%20Jumana%20Manna%20also%20took%20to%20Instagram%20to%20announce%20the%20cancellation%20of%20her%20film%20at%20the%20festival.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20acceptance%20speech%2C%20Patwardhan%20said%20that%20he%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20%E2%80%9Camplify%20all%20international%20voices%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Palestine%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20other%20ongoing%20war%20zones.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20river%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20Palestine%20will%20be%20free%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmisunderstood%20slogan%E2%80%9D%20and%20its%20real%20meaning%20%E2%80%93%20which%20he%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20call%20for%20a%20land%20where%20Muslims%2C%20Jews%2C%20Christians%20and%20all%20others%20can%20live%20together%20in%20peace%20and%20harmony%20and%20with%20equal%20rights%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20should%20be%20emphasised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatwardhan%20also%20lauded%20those%20who%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20festival%2C%20those%20who%20stayed%20back%20to%20continue%20to%20debate%20and%20those%20who%20%E2%80%9Callowed%20the%20space%E2%80%9D%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20protests%20have%20been%20non-violent.%20Non-violence%20can%20build%20a%20global%20community.%20In%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20Palestinians%20and%20Jews%20are%20marching%20together%20with%20others%20to%20demand%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20a%20just%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20acceptance%20speech%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EVasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%2FThe%20World%20is%20Family%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcceptance%20speech%20for%20Best%20Editing%20Award%20at%20IDFA%2C%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20amplify%20all%20international%20voices%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Palestine%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20other%20ongoing%20war%20zones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20river%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20Palestine%20will%20be%20free%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20misunderstood%20slogan.%20Some%20interpret%20it%20as%20a%20slogan%20calling%20for%20a%20One%20State%20solution%20and%20the%20ethnic%20cleansing%20of%20Jews.%20This%20misunderstanding%20is%20why%20the%20real%20meaning%20of%20the%20slogan%20should%20be%20explained%20and%20emphasized%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20a%20call%20for%20a%20land%20where%20Muslims%2C%20Jews%2C%20Christians%20and%20all%20others%20can%20live%20together%20in%20peace%20and%20harmony%20and%20with%20equal%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20applaud%20those%20who%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20festival%20and%20sparked%20an%20international%20debate.%20I%20applaud%20those%20who%20stayed%20back%20to%20continue%20the%20debate%20from%20within.%20And%20I%20applaud%20those%20who%20allowed%20us%20the%20space%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20protests%20have%2