E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channelnewsasia.com%2Fworld%2Fmaldives-president-elect-mohamed-muizzu-economic-challenges-foreign-policy-vision-climate-change-geopolitical-tensions-foreign-debt-election-win-office-3925021%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChannel%20News%20Asia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20new%20president%20was%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20that%20resetting%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20policy%20would%20be%20one%20of%20his%20priorities%20in%20the%20first%20100%20days%20of%20his%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20reiterated%20that%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20troops%20would%20be%20at%20the%20top%20of%20his%20agenda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20Maldives%20have%20very%20clearly%20spoken%20during%20this%20campaign%2C%20that%20they%20have%20given%20me%20a%20mandate%20of%20removing%20foreign%20military%20presence%20from%20the%20Maldives.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20India%20or%20any%20other%20country%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20Singapore-based%20news%20channel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20Maldives%20president%20has%20asked%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20troops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20June%202018%2C%20President%20Abdulla%20Yameen%20had%20refused%20to%20renew%20the%20contract%20for%20two%20advanced%20light%20helicopters%20gifted%20by%20New%20Delhi%20and%20called%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20Indian%20security%20personnel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20India%20had%20around%20six%20navy%20pilots%20and%20several%20ground%20personnel%20to%20operate%20the%20two%20choppers%2C%20which%20were%20being%20used%20as%20air%20ambulances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERelations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Maldives%20had%20already%20nosedived%20under%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20administration%2C%20but%20the%20demand%20to%20India%20to%20withdraw%20its%20personnel%20was%20not%20carried%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20months%20later%2C%20Yameen%20lost%20elections%20to%20joint%20opposition%20candidate%20Ibrahim%20Solih.%20The%20Indian%20PM%20had%20attended%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20in%20November%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20Solih%20administration%2C%20India%20has%20also%20funded%20several%20major%20projects%2C%20including%20the%20Greater%20Mal%C3%A9%20Connectivity%20project%2C%20which%20was%20touted%20as%20the%20largest%20such%20infrastructure%20development%20project%20in%20the%20Maldives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPresident%20Muizzu%20also%20underlined%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eimportance%20of%20accelerating%20the%20Greater%20Male%20Connectivity%20Project%20(GMCP)%2C%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20addressing%20and%20overcoming%20the%20issues%20delaying%20the%20project%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20readout%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700314877000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18191017%2Fs2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-president-asks-india-to-withdraw-its-troops%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20office%20of%20Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20revealed%20the%20request%2C%20there%20has%20been%20official%20silence%20from%20the%20Indian%20side.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-president-asks-india-to-withdraw-its-troops%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Workers%20trapped%20in%20collapsed%20road%20tunnel%20for%20seventh%20day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C