Hostage%20a%20%E2%80%98Mistake%E2%80%99%2C%20Reveals%20Extensive%20Details%20of%20Hostage%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18182542%2FFotoJet.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAGL3mkKQ8ng%5C%22%3EIn%20an%20extremely%20important%20and%20highly%20newsworthy%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20political%20bureau%20and%20presently%20head%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20international%20relations%20office%20in%20Doha%20has%20given%20extensive%20details%20of%20the%20hostage-prisoner%20exchange%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20are%20negotiating%20through%20the%20good%20offices%20of%20Qatar%20whilst%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20admitting%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20mistake%E2%80%9D%20to%20take%20a%20nine-month-old%20baby%20and%20an%2085-year%20old%20woman%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Musa%20Abu%20Marzouq%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20diplomats%20of%20Russia%2C%20China%2C%20Qatar%20and%20several%20European%20countries%2C%20which%20he%20did%20not%20identify%2C%20have%20been%20calling%20upon%20him%20in%20his%20office%20in%20Doha%20surreptitiously%20and%20quietly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20really%20meant%20what%20he%20was%20saying%2C%20Marzouq%20bluntly%20replied%20in%20English%3A%20%E2%80%9Cyes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2060-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20the%20questions%20were%20asked%20in%20English%20and%20translated%20into%20Arabic%20before%20Marzouq%20replied%20in%20the%20same%20language%20%E2%80%93%20though%20on%20a%20few%20occasions%20Marzouq%20himself%20replied%20in%20English%20%E2%80%93%20Marzouq%20spelt%20out%20details%20of%20the%20hostage-prisoner%20exchange%20Qatar%20is%20negotiating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Hamas%20will%20release%2050%20Israeli%20hostages%20in%20return%20for%20Israel%20releasing%20100%20Palestinian%20prisoners.%20He%20said%20this%20would%20happen%20during%20a%20five-day%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarzouq%20said%20there%20were%20two%20conditions.%20First%2C%20Hamas%20wants%20free%20movement%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20to%20move%20both%20north-to-south%20and%20south-to-north.%20He%20said%20Israel%20has%20agreed%20to%20the%20north-south%20movement%20but%20is%20so%20far%20not%20agreeing%20to%20the%20south-north%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarzouq%20said%20the%20second%20condition%20is%20that%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20airstrikes%20completely%20stopping%20during%20the%20five-day%20ceasefire%2C%20there%20should%20be%20no%20movement%20in%20the%20skies%2C%20i.e.%20no%20reconnaissance%20flights%20or%20drones.%20So%20far%20Israel%20has%20not%20agreed%20to%20this%20condition%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%20%E2%80%93%20and%20you%20must%20see%20this%20for%20yourself%20%E2%80%93%20Marzouq%20clearly%20seemed%20to%20contradict%20what%20Hamas%20spokesperson%20Osama%20Hamdan%20told%20the%20BBC%20on%20the%20November%2016%20when%20he%20claimed%20none%20of%20the%20approximately%20240%20Israeli%20hostages%20are%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Marzouq%20said%20Hamas%20cannot%20compile%20a%20list%20of%20hostages%20until%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20which%20clearly%20suggests%20that%20there%20are%20hostages%20in%20its%20custody.%20Otherwise%20the%20question%20of%20compiling%20a%20list%20does%20not%20arise.%20This%20was%20repeatedly%20pointed%20out%20to%20him%20and%20he%20said%20(from%20memory)%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthat%E2%80%99s%20the%20conclusion%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20repeatedly%20clear%20that%20he%20was%20only%20speaking%20for%20himself%2C%20Marzouq%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20ideal%20and%20only%20solution%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20one-state%20solution%20where%20Jews%20and%20Muslims%2C%20Israelis%20and%20Palestinians%20live%20together%20in%20one%20country%20with%20equal%20rights%20and%20equal%20privileges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20repeated%20questioning%2C%20Marzouq%20would%20not%20reveal%20or%2C%20perhaps%2C%20I%20should%20say%20confirm%2C%20that%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20political%20bureau%2C%20shares%20the%20same%20belief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20an%20awful%20lot%20in%20this%20interview%20that%20is%20very%20newsworthy%20and%20very%20important%20because%20it%20reveals%20things%20for%20the%20first%20time%20as%20well%20as%20has%20Hamas%20accept%20its%20mistakes.%20So%20that%20I%20do%20not%20misconstrue%20and%20misrepresent%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20mislead%20you%2C%20I%20will%20stop%20at%20this%20point%20and%20let%20you%20view%20the%20interview%20for%20yourself%20and%20hear%20Marzouq%20in%20his%20own%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20will%20give%20you%20the%20full%20list%20of%20questions%20put%20to%20Marzouq.%20Here%20they%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%E2%80%99s%20start%20with%20October%207.%20How%20does%20Hamas%20justify%20killing%201%2C200%20people%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20whom%20were%20innocent%20civilians%20and%20often%20young%20children%20or%20even%20babies%20as%20well%20as%20elderly%20people%20in%20their%2070s%20and%2080s%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20considers%20this%20utterly%20condemnable%20and%20completely%20unforgiveable.%20How%20do%20you%20justify%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E2.%3C%2Fb%3E%20Just%20look%20at%20the%20atrocities%20committed.%20Almost%20300%20young%20people%20enjoying%20the%20Supernova%20music%20festival%20were%20literally%20butchered.%20What%20had%20they%20done%20to%20deserve%20being%20killed%20in%20this%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20worst%20part%20is%20that%20the%20Hamas%20gunmen%20took%20pleasure%20in%20what%20they%20were%20doing.%20CBS%20News%20reports%20the%20Israelis%20have%20a%20video%20of%20a%20gunman%20called%20Mahmood%20who%20rang%20up%20his%20father%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CDad%2C%20I%20killed%20ten%20(Jews)%20with%20my%20bare%20hands%20%E2%80%A6%20please%20be%20proud%20of%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20just%20barbaric%20savagery%2C%20I%20imagine%20most%20Palestinians%20would%20be%20embarrassed%20by%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E4.%3C%2Fb%3E%20Look%20at%20the%20sort%20of%20people%20you%20have%20taken%20as%20hostages.%20A%20nine-month%20old%20baby%20and%20an%2085-year-old%20woman.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20of%20the%20hostages%20are%20elderly%20who%20need%20medicines%20and%20could%20die%20without%20them.%20And%20you%20have%20held%20on%20to%20them%20for%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E5.%3C%2Fb%3E%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20even%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20of%20the%20Palestine%20Authority%20does%20not%20defend%20what%20Hamas%20has%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20his%20initial%20comment%20before%20he%20amended%20it%20for%20political%20reasons%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20policies%20and%20actions%20of%20Hamas%20do%20not%20represent%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Palestine%20Liberation%20Organization%20represent(s)%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20as%20their%20sole%20legitimate%20representative%20and%20not%20%E2%80%A6%20any%20other%20organization.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20even%20your%20fellow%20Palestinians%20have%20sharply%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20Hamas%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20poll%20done%20by%20Arab%20Barometer%2C%20research%20for%20which%20concluded%20on%20the%20October%206%20and%20was%20recently%20published%20by%20%3Cem%3EForeign%20Affairs%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20shows%20that%20distrust%20of%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20is%20very%20high.%20Forty-four%20percent%20had%20no%20trust%20at%20all%20whilst%2023%25%20said%20they%20have%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20trust.%20That%E2%80%99s%2067%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20after%20the%20devastation%2C%20destruction%20and%20deaths%20that%20your%20October%207%20strike%20has%20brought%20upon%20Gaza%2C%20if%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20blame%20you%20for%20what%E2%80%99s%20happened%2C%20support%20for%20Hamas%20could%20collapse%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Alright%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20a%20second%20issue.%20There%20are%20a%20spate%20of%20reports%20that%20Qatar%20is%20arranging%20an%20exchange%20of%20hostages%20for%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20and%20Reuters%20has%20said%20that%20Hamas%20has%20agreed%20to%20the%20broad%20outline%20of%20this%20deal%20and%20now%20Qatar%20is%20waiting%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20broad%20agreement.%20Can%20you%20confirm%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20Thursday%20(November%2016)%2C%20Osama%20Hamdan%2C%20a%20Hamas%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20on%20the%20BBC%20that%20none%20of%20the%20approximately%20240%20Israeli%20hostages%20are%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Hamas.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20on%20two%20occasions%2C%20Hamas%20had%20wanted%20to%20return%20the%20hostages%20to%20Israel%2C%20but%20the%20obstacle%20was%20from%20the%20Israeli%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20can%20you%20confirm%20this%20and%20what%20further%20details%20can%20you%20give%20me%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20least%20on%20two%20occasions%2C%20Israel%20has%20agreed%20to%20a%20disproportionately%20large%20exchange%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20in%20return%20for%20its%20hostages.%20In%202011%2C%20Israel%20exchanged%201%2C027%20prisoners%20for%20just%20one%20soldier.%20In%201985%2C%20it%20exchanged%201%2C150%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20for%20three%20Israeli%20soldiers%20captured%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20you%20hoping%20or%20trying%20for%20something%20similar%20this%20time%20around%3F%20The%20exchange%20of%20all%207%2C000%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20in%20Israeli%20jails%20for%20the%20240%20hostages%20you%20hold%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Before%20we%20end%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20look%20to%20the%20future%20to%20the%20extent%20we%20can.%20In%202017%2C%20Hamas%20changed%20its%20charter%20and%20was%20willing%20to%20accept%20an%20Israeli%20state%20alongside%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20without%20officially%20recognising%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20what%E2%80%99s%20happened%20over%20the%20last%20six%20weeks%2C%20when%20over%2012%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20perhaps%2029%2C000%20injured%2C%20can%20you%20go%20back%20to%20this%20position%3F%20Or%20is%20this%20door%20closed%20forever%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E11.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Are%20you%20saying%20to%20me%20that%20your%20position%20is%20that%20from%20the%20Jordan%20River%20to%20the%20Mediterranean%20Sea%2C%20the%20whole%20land%20must%20be%20Palestine%3F%20Because%20that%20means%20the%20annihilation%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E12.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Will%20Arab%20countries%20like%20Egypt%2C%20Jordan%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20Morocco%20accept%20this%3F%20After%20all%20they%20have%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Israel.%20And%20what%20about%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20which%20was%20very%20keen%20to%20join%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAGL3mkKQ8ng%3Fsi%3DqQgWske_L2QmyG7o%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700312452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18182542%2FFotoJet.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fsenior-hamas-leader-admits-hostage-mistake-reveals-hostage-deal-details%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Musa%20Abu%20Marzouq%20said%20Hamas%20will%20release%2050%20Israeli%20hostages%20in%20return%20for%20Israel%20releasing%20100%20Palestinian%20prisoners.%20He%20said%20this%20would%20happen%20during%20a%20five-day%20ceasefire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fsenior-hamas-leader-admits-hostage-mistake-reveals-hostage-deal-details%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IAF%20Lands%20%E2%80%98Super%20Hercules%E2%80%99%20Military%20Transport%20Aircraft%20on%20Unfeasible%20Strip%20for%20Tunnel%20Rescue%20Mission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18180433%2Fimage-1522.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20yet%20another%20instance%20of%20operational%20daredevilry%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20successfully%20landed%20two%20of%20its%20Lockheed%20Martin%20C-130J-30%20%E2%80%98Super%20Hercules%E2%80%99%20military%20transport%20aircraft%20at%20a%20rudimentary%20and%20unfeasible%20air%20strip%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20This%20mission%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20inclement%20weather%2C%20to%20deliver%20heavy%20engineering%20equipment%20to%20help%20rescue%20workers%20trapped%20inside%20a%20nearby%20under-construction%20mountain%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20the%20IAF%20said%20that%20its%20two%20C-130J-30%E2%80%99s%20executed%20three%20sorties%20to%20the%20rudimentary%20Dharasu%20advanced%20landing%20ground%20(ALG)%20on%20November%2015.%20This%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20%E2%80%98reduced%20visibility%20conditions%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20ferry%2027.5%20tons%20of%20machinery%20needed%20to%20extricate%2041%20construction%20workers%2C%20entombed%20since%20Sunday%2C%20in%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20being%20built%20on%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Yamunotri%20National%20Highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20narrow%20and%20undeveloped%203%2C600%20feet%20ALG%2C%20located%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%203%2C000%20ft%2C%20some%2030%20kilometre%20from%20the%20mishap%20site%2C%20had%20earlier%20been%20declared%20%E2%80%98unsuitable%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20IAF%20for%20C-130J-30%20operations.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20urgency%20in%20reaching%20the%20critical%20equipment%20to%20rescue%20teams%20spurred%20the%20IAF%20and%20its%20pilots%20to%2C%20yet%20again%2C%20exploit%20their%20jugaad%20or%20innovative%20skills%20and%20fabled%20derring-do%20to%20professionally%20vindicate%20their%20mission%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20undertaking%20the%20delivery%20flight%2C%20an%20IAF%20helicopter%20with%20C-130J-30%20pilots%20on%20board%20had%20executed%20an%20exhaustive%20recce%20of%20the%20ALG%E2%80%99s%20questionable%20condition%20and%20the%20many%20obstructions%20it%20posed%2C%20before%20eventually%20undertaking%20the%20equipment%20delivery%20mission.%20Thereafter%2C%20varied%20aspects%20of%20the%20reconnaissance%20were%20suitably%20%E2%80%98war-gamed%E2%80%99%2C%20taking%20all%20impediments%20into%20consideration%2C%20and%20an%20operational%20plan%20was%20then%20formalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quasi-military%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%2C%20or%20BRO%2C%20was%20roped%20in%20to%20clear%20the%20ALG%20of%20thick%20undergrowth%20and%20shrubbery%2C%20and%20in%20the%20best%20tradition%20of%20jugaad%20that%20defines%20a%20wide%20spectrum%20of%20its%20operational%20activity%2C%20as%20well%20as%20that%20of%20the%20Indian%20military%2C%20it%20also%20constructed%20a%20makeshift%20mud%20ramp%20to%20substitute%20for%20specialised%20off-loading%20equipment%2C%20simply%20unavailable%20at%20the%20remote%20ALG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20inputs%20from%20the%20helicopter%20reconnaissance%20mission%20over%20Dharasu%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98non-routine%20critical%20delivery%E2%80%99%20mission%20featured%20two%20C-130J-30%E2%80%99s%20from%20the%20IAFs%2077%20%E2%80%98Veiled%20Vipers%E2%80%99%20Squadron%20at%20Hindan%2C%20on%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20outskirts%2C%20and%20was%20ably%20completed%20in%20under%20five%20hours.%20The%20IAF%20declared%20that%20the%20entire%20operation%20was%20underscored%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98calculated%20approach%20and%20adequate%20risk%20mitigation%E2%80%99.%20Its%20success%2C%20it%20added%2C%20stemmed%20from%20%E2%80%98pinpoint%20execution%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20other%2C%20larger%2C%20Boeing%20C-17%20Globemaster%20III%20air%20lifters%2C%20too%2C%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20tunnel%20rescue%20operations.%20One%20of%20them%20shipped%2022%20tons%20of%20heavy%20equipment%20from%20Indore%20to%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20capital%20Dehradun%2C%20from%20where%20it%20was%20shipped%20to%20Dharasu%20by%20road%2C%20for%20onward%20transshipment%20to%20the%20accident%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAFs%20daredevil%20Dharasu%20delivery%20operation%20was%20reminiscent%20of%20its%2017%20daring%20flights%2C%20featuring%20C-130J-30%E2%80%99s%20and%20C-17s%2C%20which%20were%20undertaken%20earlier%20this%20year%20as%20part%20of%20Operation%20Kaveri%20to%20repatriate%20thousands%20of%20Indians%20from%20war-torn%20Sudan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fiaf-c17-aircraft-rescue-mission-sudan%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20some%20of%20these%20C-130J-30%20flights%2C%20which%20were%20executed%20in%20pitch%20darkness%2C%20with%20calmness%20and%20dexterity%20on%20the%20unfamiliar%20Wadi%20Sayyidna%20airstrip%20that%20had%20neither%20any%20navigational%20approach%20aids%20nor%20critical%20landings%20lights%2C%20some%2040%20km%20north%20of%20the%20Sudanese%20capital%20Khartoum%2C%20wracked%20by%20civil%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20fleet%20of%2012%20C-130J-30s%2C%20inducted%20into%20service%202011%20onwards%2C%20are%20split%20between%20the%2077%20Squadron%20at%20Hindan%20and%20the%2087%20%E2%80%98Wings%20of%20Valour%E2%80%99%20Squadron%20at%20Panagarh%20in%20the%20east%2C%20from%20where%20they%20support%20the%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20deployment%20along%20the%20disputed%20line%20of%20actual%20control%20(LAC)%20with%20China.%20The%20IAFs%2011%20C-17s%20operated%20as%20part%20of%20No%2081%20%E2%80%9CSkylords%E2%80%99%20squadron%2C%20also%20from%20Hindan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20aircraft%20types%20were%20acquired%20via%20the%20Foreign%20Military%20Sales%20(FMS)%20route%2C%20with%20the%20C-130J-30%E2%80%99s%20costing%20around%20%242-2.5%20billion%20and%20the%20C-17s%20priced%20at%20around%20%244.1%20billion.%20In%20recent%20times%2C%20both%20platforms%20had%20been%20instrumental%20in%20transporting%20army%20personnel%20%E2%80%93%20and%20their%20assorted%20assets-like%20tanks%20and%20infantry%20combat%20vehicles%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20LAC%20to%20counter%20the%20ongoing%20three-year-long%20face%20off%20with%20China%E2%80%99s%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%20had%20last%20acquired%20some%2070-odd%20second-hand%20twin-piston%20engine%20Fairchild%20C-119%20%E2%80%98Flying%20Boxcars%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20US%20in%20the%201950s%2C%20after%20which%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20Washington%20deteriorated%20and%20those%20with%20Moscow%20proliferated%2C%20lasting%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%20era%2C%20which%20ended%20only%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%20The%20C-119s%2C%20however%2C%20were%20retired%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20following%20their%20extensive%20employment%20in%20two%20wars%20with%20Pakistan%20in%201965%20and%201971.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20for%20over%20five%20decades%20thereafter%2C%20the%20IAF%20remained%20dependent%20almost%20entirely%20on%20legacy%20Soviet-origin%20transport%20platforms.%20This%20was%20in%20addition%20to%20combat%20aircraft-like%20the%20Ilyushin%20Il-76s%20and%20Antonov%20An-32s%2C%20which%20a%20cross-section%20of%20IAF%20pilots%20maintained%20had%20recently%20been%20%E2%80%98technologically%20outmanoeuvred%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20newly%20inducted%20US%20transports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fully%20automated%2C%20state-of-the-art%20flight%20decks%20of%20both%20the%20US%20models%20fitted%20with%20%2B4%20generation%20avionics%20were%20far%20superior%20to%20those%20of%20the%20two%20Soviet%20transports%2C%20making%20them%20relatively%20effortless%20to%20operate%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20former%20IAF%20transport%20pilot%20said%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20identified.%20Besides%2C%20the%20US%20platforms%20were%20%E2%80%98significantly%E2%80%99%20more%20fuel%20efficient%2C%20requiring%20a%20smaller%2C%20three-person%20crew%20%E2%80%93%20two%20pilots%20and%20a%20loadmaster%20%E2%80%93%20to%20operate%2C%20compared%20to%20five%20personnel%20needed%20for%20an%20Il-76%20and%20four%20for%20an%20An-32%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20ease%20of%20operation%20both%20in%20the%20air%20and%20on%20ground%2C%20the%20US%20transports%20had%20a%2012-week%20maintenance%20cycle%2C%20which%20was%20almost%20three%20times%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20the%20Il-76s%20and%20even%20the%2060-70%20retrofitted%20and%20upgraded%20twin-turboprop%20An-32s%2C%20both%20of%20which%20required%20regular%20servicing%20every%20three%20to%20four%20weeks%2C%20said%20the%20C-17%20pilot%20quoted%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20total%20technical%20life%20cycle%20of%20C-130J-30%20and%20C-17%20engines%2C%20too%2C%20is%20notably%20higher%20%E2%80%93%20almost%2010%20times%20more%20than%20that%20of%20the%20fuel-intensive%20Soviet%20aircraft%20power%20packs%2C%E2%80%9D%20retired%20Air%20Marshal%20V.K.%20Bhatia%20said.%20This%20operational%20aspect%20increased%20platform%20efficiency%20and%20considerably%20reduced%20maintenance%20and%20operating%20costs%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20by%20undertaking%20the%20Dharasu%20delivery%20mission%2C%20the%20IAF%20had%20%E2%80%98stretched%E2%80%99%20the%20C-130J-30%E2%80%99s%20operational%20envelope%2C%20possibly%20even%20a%20little%20beyond%20what%20its%20manufacturers%20Lockheed%20had%20anticipated%20and%20could%2C%20in%20time%2C%20further%20boost%20the%20transport%20platform%E2%80%99s%20commercial%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20as%20the%20adage%20goes%2C%20the%20only%20way%20to%20discover%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20possible%2C%20is%20to%20go%20beyond%20them%20into%20the%20impossible%3B%20or%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20near-impossible%2C%20an%20endeavour%20in%20which%20the%20Indian%20military%20excels%20on%20multiple%20fronts%20in%20exploiting%20its%20assorted%20platforms%20and%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700312417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18180433%2Fimage-1522.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fiaf-lands-super-hercules-military-transport-aircraft-on-unfeasible-strip-for-tunnel-rescue-mission%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20narrow%20and%20undeveloped%203%2C600%20feet%20advanced%20landing%20ground%20had%20earlier%20been%20declared%20%E2%80%98unsuitable%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20IAF%20for%20C-130J-30%20operations.%20But%20despite%20that%2C%20the%20IAF%20executed%20a%20perilous%20mission%20to%20deliver%20crucial%20equipment%20for%20rescuing%20trapped%20workers%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20mountain%20tunnel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fiaf-lands-super-hercules-military-transport-aircraft-on-unfeasible-strip-for-tunnel-rescue-mission%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Palestine%2C%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20Western%20Liberal%E2%80%99s%20Burden%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17151101%2FF8PxlS-a4AAO8nS.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20comedian%20Jeremy%20McLellan%E2%80%99s%20tone%20is%20clipped%20and%20cheery%20as%20he%20presents%20his%20brief%20recent%20video%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%9910%20Ways%20to%20Support%20Israel%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98.%20%3C%2Fem%3EA%20couple%20of%20minutes%20into%20the%20presentation%2C%20the%20melancholy%20figure%20of%20a%2