7-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FYa_All-1-1700226597-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334382%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYa_All%E2%80%99s%20Transgender%20Football%20Team%20has%20been%20taking%20the%20lead%20in%20using%20Football%20for%20Recovery%20from%20the%20trauma%20of%20conflict.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EComing%20full%20circle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lengths%20Sadam%20has%20gone%20to%20create%20safe%20spaces%20for%20queer%20youth%20in%20Manipur%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20remarkable.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20Amazon%20Prime%20series%20Rainbow%20Rishta%20shed%20light%20on%20his%20personal%20life%2C%20there%20were%20moments%20where%20he%20was%20clearly%20uncomfortable%20talking%20about%20it.%20But%20what%20the%20process%20of%20shooting%20the%20documentary%20did%20was%20help%20him%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20the%20entire%20shooting%20process%20helped%20me%20realise%20is%20that%20I%20had%20drowned%20myself%20in%20work%20and%20as%20a%20result%20became%20very%20lonely%20again.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20I%20had%20forgotten%20to%20live%20my%20personal%20life.%20I%20had%20to%20ask%20myself%20who%20I%20was%20without%20my%20work.%20The%20series%20compelled%20me%20to%20have%20these%20conversations%20about%20myself%20and%20also%20with%20my%20parents%20who%20were%20informed%20of%20the%20shoot%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20writers%20and%20directors%20were%20helping%20me%20talk%20about%20my%20past%20and%20helping%20my%20parents%20talk%20about%20their%20son%2C%20and%20in%20that%20process%2C%20even%20though%20my%20coming%20out%20was%20a%20tragic%20episode%2C%20this%20felt%20like%20a%20real%20coming%20out%20moment.%20People%20from%20all%20over%20India%20are%20now%20connecting%20