or%20Vihaan%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20they%20spin%20webs%2C%20and%20hunt%20their%20prey%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20so%20cool%3F%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20He%20recalls%20spending%20hours%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332890%2Findian-photographers-pictures-military-navy-wildlife-oceans-astronomy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapturing%20their%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20childhood%20summer%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20was%20only%20natural%20that%20the%20young%20boy%20sat%20down%2C%20and%20watched%20the%20spider%20weave%20a%20wheel-shaped%20web%2C%20entangling%20any%20prey%20that%20dared%20to%20come%20too%20close.%20And%20soon%20he%20got%20clicking.%20%E2%80%9CI%20must%20have%20clicked%20over%20200%20pictures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20among%20them%20was%20the%20winning%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vihaan's%20winning%20shot%20in%20the%20'10%20years%20and%20under'%20category%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334317%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVihaan%E2%80%99s%20winning%20shot%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9910%20years%20and%20under%E2%80%99%20category%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vihaan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20caught%20the%20judges%E2%80%99%20eye%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317185%2Fbollywood-celebrity-photographer-munna-thaakur-recalls-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20composition%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20image.%20As%20Dhritiman%20Mukherjee%2C%20Wildlife%20and%20Conservation%20Photographer%20and%20Competition%20Judge%2C%20commented%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20image%20conveys%20so%20many%20interesting%20things%20to%20me.%20It%20talks%20about%20coexistence%20very%20nicely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inclusion%20of%20a%20historic%20sculpture%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20adds%20a%20different%20dimension%20to%20the%20concept.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20here%20we%20are%2C%20seeing%20a%20spider%20%E2%80%94%20a%20smaller%20and%20less%20attended%20life%20form.%20So%2C%20for%20me%2C%20this%20one%20served%20the%20purpose%20of%20art%2C%20concept%2C%20conservation%20and%20science%20very%20nicely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFreezing%20moments%20in%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summer%20of%202020%20was%20a%20life-changing%20one%20for%20Vihaan%2C%20who%20had%20just%20discovered%20the%20wonders%20of%20the%20camera.%20His%20father%E2%80%99s%20farm%20in%20Basavani%20village%2C%20which%20lay%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20was%20akin%20to%20a%20sanctuary%20for%20Vihaan.%20There%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw