FMy-work-view-15-1699023227-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-15-1699023227-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUday%20Bhatia%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20student%20from%20Delhi%2C%20has%20built%20a%20sustainable%20lighting%20solution%20for%20rural%20India.%20His%20%E2%80%98Uday%20Electric%E2%80%99%20bulbs%20provide%20a%20power%20backup%20of%208-10%20hours%20in%20case%20of%20a%20power%20cut.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20financial%20literacy%20workshop%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333600%2Fuday-bhatia-uday-electric-inverter-bulb-power-cuts-uttar-pradesh-uttarakhand-power-crisis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUday%20Bhatia%20%3C%2Fa%3Efound%20that%20there%20were%20frequent%20outages%2C%20for%20almost%208-10%20hours%20daily%2C%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20children%20to%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wanted%20to%20develop%20an%20affordable%20solution%20for%20these%20children%2C%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20inverters%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20an%20inverter%20bulb%20that%20can%20provide%20a%20backup%20of%20almost%2010%20hours%20in%20case%20of%20a%20power%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2024%20prototypes%2C%20thousands%20of%20hours%2C%20and%20eight%20months%2C%20the%2018-year-old%20built%20the%20solution%20%E2%80%93%20through%20his%20venture%20%E2%80%98Uday%20Electric%E2%80%99.%20The%20bulb%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20250%20and%20he%20started%20sales%20from%20May%202022.%20The%20bulbs%20come%20with%20a%201-year%20warranty.%20The%20tagline%20of%20the%20company%20is%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBijli%20gul%20phir%20bhi%20ujjala%20full%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Even%20if%20the%20power%20is%20cut%2C%20there%20will%20still%20be%20light).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20so%20far%20sold%20over%207%2C000%20units%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20to%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Delhi.%20Of%20these%2C%20950%20units%20were%20donated%20to%20households%20in%20the%20Kabadi%20Bazar%2C%20Dehradun%2C%20through%20Aasra%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%227%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDivaa%20Uthkarsha%2C%2015%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20738px)%20100vw%2C%20738px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa2-1688482712.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22738%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa2-1688482712.jpg%20738w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa2-1688482712-138x300.jpg%20138w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa2-1688482712-472x1024.jpg%20472w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa2-1688482712-708x1536.jpg%20708w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa2-1688482712-150x325.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322765%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDivaa%20Uthkarsha%20is%20creating%20awareness%20about%20type%201%20diabetes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20changed%20for%20Divaa%20at%2012%2C%20when%20her%20younger%20brother%20Surya%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20Type-1%20diabetes.%20Despite%20having%20doctor%20parents%20and%20access%20to%20the%20best%20healthcare%2C%20they%20faced%20several%20challenges%20including%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20school%20children%20may%20not%20be%20well-informed%20and%20co