he%20knew%20that%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20was%20for%20the%20greater%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20collector%20saw%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20help%20Srikanth%20recover%20the%20land%20and%20build%20a%20forest.%20Srikanth%20got%20back%20the%20encroached%2025-acre%20land%2C%20cleaned%20it%20and%20planted%207%2C000%20trees%20in%20the%20area.%20He%20spent%20more%20than%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20collector%20gave%20me%2025%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20workers%20to%20help%20me%20with%20the%20work.%20In%20a%20year%2C%20the%20forest%20grew%20well%20and%20became%20home%20to%20many%20birds%20and%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srikanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHe%20planted%20native%20trees%20and%20fruits%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20like%20jamun%2C%20peepal%2C%20fig%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201040px)%20100vw%2C%201040px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srikanth%20invested%20Rs%201.5%20lakhs%20to%20build%20the%20forest%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426.jpeg%201040w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Im